<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Welcome to the Newsletter - ExecStream</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #2d2d2d;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #0066cc;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #0066cc;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e6ed;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #f1f3f6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>ExecStream</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>You're Subscribed!</h2>
        <p>Thanks for signing up for the ExecStream newsletter.</p>
        <p>
          From now on, you’ll receive the latest insights, trends, and updates
          delivered straight to your inbox.
        </p>
        <p>
          We’re glad to have you with us. If you ever wish to unsubscribe,
          you’ll find a link at the bottom of our emails.
        </p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Welcome aboard,<br />The ExecStream Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">© <%= year %> ExecStream. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
